<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/not_found.css" />
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flash-messages">
      <% if (flash.success) { %>
            <div class="flash-message success"><%= flash.success %></div>
      <% } %>   
      <% if (message) { %>
        <div class="flash-message success"><%= message %></div>
  <% } %>   
      </div>  
    <h1>Welcome to Our Website</h1>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        At Our Website, we are dedicated to providing top-notch services and
        solutions to our clients. Our team of experts is passionate about
        delivering excellence in every project we undertake. With years of
        experience and a commitment to innovation, we strive to exceed
        expectations and create a lasting impact in the industry.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Services</h2>
      <p>
        Our range of services is designed to cater to diverse needs and
        requirements. From web development and design to digital marketing and
        consulting, we have you covered. We believe in understanding our
        clients' goals and tailoring our solutions to help them achieve success.
        With a customer-centric approach, we aim to build long-lasting
        relationships.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Get in touch with us today to explore how we can assist you. Our
        friendly team is ready to answer any queries and provide detailed
        information about our services. Don't hesitate to reach out to us via
        phone, email, or by filling out the contact form on our website. We look
        forward to hearing from you soon!
      </p>
    </div>
 
    <form action="/shop/products" method="get">
      <button class="primary-button">Learn More</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <%- include('../includes/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
